<p>Once our <strong>Stage 1</strong> mastering process has been completed and signed off by the client, our software automatically derives masters specifically designed to meet the specifications of each planned distribution endpoint:</p>

<h3 id="mastered-for-digital">Mastered for Digital</h3>

<p>To ensure compliance with digital streaming endpoints, all of our digital stream masters are output to EBU R128 specifications. This means we target a -60 LUFS noise threshold, do not let true peaks exceed -2dBTP, and maintain deviances that do not exceed Â±0.5 LU.</p>

